column5: Got out today on my own and landed a couple decent bows. the water was mint but not many fish around today.    BB
nothing wrong with that piece O fish!
Great report and pic bbnotty Nice looking bow... congratulation Thanks for sharing Leechman

Berg, your a machine !!!! Nice fish, L M A O when I heard what you got it on !!!...You didn't miss much up north...Must have walked 10km today, and fished dawn till dusk, only producing 2 fish  ... There wasn't a CN rail within 2 hours , so atleast the scenery was nice
Thanks guys. Eh Dave i'll try anything  , oh and don't you know that bows love the sound of trains?
That's one more fish than I caught yesterday!  Great looking fish!  I gotta hit the tribs again soon...been a few weeks...and I'm getting the itch!!!
Indeed they do my friend, indeed they do
